item.title: the first blog post
item.description: Episode 1 or Why the heck am I making a blog, this is such a stupid idea, like what if colleges or future recruiters look at this and I look like an idiot? Dear reader, if you ever read this, you may ask yourself, “What am I doing here? Why am I reading the failed blog of a highschooler?1 He can’t even gain a single star on Github. He can’t even figure out how to build anything without Stack Overflow.
